ZH: 1. 永不放弃，成功就在不远处。
EN: Never give up, success is just around the corner.
ZH: 2. 他永不会原谅你的背叛。
EN: He will never forgive your betrayal.
ZH: 3. 永不停止学习，才能获得进步。
EN: Never stop learning in order to make progress.
ZH: 4. 他们永不会忘记那个特殊的日子。
EN: They will never forget that special day.
ZH: 5. 我会永不放弃对你的爱。
EN: I will never give up on my love for you.
ZH: 6. 永不言败是成功的秘诀之一。
EN: Never say die is one of the secrets to success.
ZH: 7. 这份信念将永不熄灭。
EN: This belief will never fade away.
ZH: 8. 我永不会忘记我们在那里度过的美好时光。
EN: I will never forget the wonderful time we spent there.
ZH: 9. 她永不会原谅你对她的伤害。
EN: She will never forgive you for hurting her.
ZH: 10. 永不退缩，战胜一切困难。
EN: Never back down, overcome all obstacles.
ZH: 11. 他们永不会相遇，因为他们生活在不同的国家。
EN: They will never meet because they live in different countries.
ZH: 12. 永不迟到是他的一贯作风。
EN: Never being late is his consistent style.
ZH: 13. 我决心要永不低头。
EN: I am determined to never bow down.
ZH: 14. 我们应该永不停止追求梦想。
EN: We should never stop pursuing our dreams.
ZH: 15. 他们的友谊将永不磨灭。
EN: Their friendship will never fade away.
ZH: 16. 永不言败，尽力去争取。
EN: Never give up, strive for the best.
ZH: 17. 她的美丽将永不凋谢。
EN: Her beauty will never wither.
ZH: 18. 不管遇到多大的困难，我们永不退缩。
EN: No matter how big the difficulty is, we will never back down.
ZH: 19. 家乡的风景永不变化。
EN: The scenery of my hometown never changes.
ZH: 20. 我永不会忘记他对我所做的一切。
EN: I will never forget everything he has done for me.
